#-----------------------------------
# Required SDKs:
#-----------------------------------
Adobe AIR SDK: http://www.adobe.com/devnet/air/air-sdk-download.html‎

For Android usage:
Android SDK: http://developer.android.com/sdk/‎

#-----------------------------------
# Required environment variables:
#-----------------------------------

$AIR_HOME -> points to installed AIR SDK 3.6
$ANDROID_SDK -> points to installed Android SDK

#-----------------------------------
# Common commands:
#-----------------------------------

# Compile for web
#  - can access at file://.../as3client/index.html
#  - to see log output, requires http://.../as3client/index.html
./builderoo.rb -compile -config debug
view index.html in browser

# Compile .apk for android
./builderoo.rb -compile -config debug -package

# Compile .apk for android, install, and watch log output (via adb)
./builderoo.rb -compile -config debug -package -install -trace

